SUBSTITUTE FOR
SENATE BILL NO. 418
A bill to amend 1982 PA 250, entitled
"Child abuse and neglect prevention act,"
by amending the title and sections 2, 3, 4, 9, 10, and 12 (MCL
722.602, 722.603, 722.604, 722.609, 722.610, and 722.612), section
2 as amended by 2018 PA 60 and section 4 as amended by 2005 PA 82.
THE PEOPLE OF THE STATE OF MICHIGAN ENACT:
1 TITLE
2 An act to establish the state child abuse and neglect
3 prevention children trust Michigan board; to provide the powers and
4 duties of the state child abuse and neglect prevention children
5 trust Michigan board; and to prescribe the powers and duties of
6 certain state departments.and local governmental officers and
7 entities.
